snippet.title: [No Comment] Kentucky Route Zero - Here and There Along The Echo
snippet.description:
Here and There Along The Echo
A Guide to the Echo River for Drifters and Pilgrims
http://kentuckyroutezero.com/here-and-there-along-the-echo/

[Edit May 18, 2020] Since I've finally finished the whole Kentucky Route Zero series, if you're watching through the playlist this video is not essential viewing. It gives some background info but nothing too vital to the story.
Also for all the people coming to this from wherever it's been linked that has given it so many views, why not check out the whole Kentucky Route Zero playlist. The whole game is, IMHO, way better than this one phone.]

Sometimes, the phone also calls you: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9hvbmneggig
